quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  51,52,"Ko wano non. Nulaa…óo araali e …ďen adinoo…ďe …ďe, si wanaa …ďe wi'ay : \"Ko mbileejo maa feetu…óo"
  51,53,"Hara …ďe wasondir e …óum? Ko woni kon, …ďee ko yim…ďe bewu…ďe"
  51,54,"Runto …ďe, a felnaaki [e fiia…ď…ďe]"
  51,55,"Waajo tun; sabu waajagol ngol, hino nafa gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  51,56,"Mi tagiraali jinna e yim…ďe, si wanaa fii yo …ďe rewan"
  51,57,Mi …óa…ď…ďiraa …ďe arsike; Mi …óa…ď…ďaa yo …ďe √Īammina
  51,58,"Pellet, ko Allah woni arsikoowo On, Jom cemmbe tii…óu…óe"
  51,59,"Haray hino woodani …ďen too√Īu…ďe, bakkaat yeru bakkaat nanndo ma…ď…ďe'en, wata …ďe hawju"
  51,60,"Bone woodanii …ďen yeddu…ďe, e nden √Ďalaande ma…ď…ďe nde …ďe kammbanaa"
  52,1,"Mi woondirii [Fello] Tuuri ngon"
  52,2,E Deftere winndaande nden
  52,3,e …óeri fontaa…ói
  52,4,E Suudu wuurniraandu ndun
  52,5,E Kippoodi toowundi ndin
  52,6,E maayo heewuno ngon
  52,7,"Pellet, lepte Joomi maa …óen ko yanooje"
  52,8,Alaa du√Īoowo …óe
  52,9,√Ďalnde kammu ngun dillirta dillere
  52,10,pelle …óen wona e yahugol
  52,11,"haray nden √Īalnde, bone woodanii fennu…ďe …ďen"
  52,12,"…ďen wonu…ďe e jumpugol, hi…ďe fija"
  52,13,√Ďalnde …ďe du√Īiroytee doole ka Yiite Jahannama du√Īannde
  52,14,"[∆Āe wi'anee] : \"Ko ngee Yiite woni ko fennayno…óon"
